Model<-augment(Cijena2)
 # dijagram raspršenja reziduala
ggplot(data = Model, aes(x = .fitted, y = .resid)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_hline(yintercept = 0, linetype = "dashed", color = "lightcoral") +
  xlab("Fitted values") +
  ylab("Residuals")

# qq dijagram reziduala 
DijagramReziduala <- ggplot(Model, aes(sample =.resid))
DijagramReziduala+ stat_qq_point(size = 2) + 
  stat_qq_line() +
  xlab("Theoretical Quantiles") + ylab("Sample Quantiles")
